  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> To be honest, I don't see the benefit of PostCSS compared to SASS for what we need.\n\nI would say, the same as using babel instead of coffeescript. Write for the future, in something close to a standard. Feature-wise it will not change much, so ok to do a Sass version first if it's what we're more proficient in.\n",
